item.title: By: Sarah Cosper
item.dc:creator: Sarah Cosper
item.description:
In reply to <a href="/suggestion-box/#comment-166">Denys</a>.
You might need a whole new skin regimen. Sometimes, we think it's one thing causing our problems, and it's something else. I would do some research into products you want to try, and then go to Sephora and get samples. You can find out what's worth your money that way. That's what I do.
item.content:encoded:
